		- coverity.mktoweb.com

			- softwareintegrity


	Nonfunctional subdomains:

		- (www.) ¹
		- scan5 ²

	¹ Refused
	² Redirects to http...:8080


	Problematic subdomains:

		- autodiscover ¹
		- blog ¹
		- softwareintegrity ²

